## 7. Hour-by-hour execution schedule

**Assumption:** ~24 hours wall clock, one day + overnight. Adjust if the window is different.

| Hour | Parallel tracks | Deliverable |
|---|---|---|
| **T+0 – T+1** | sde: scaffold repo + `.env` + git + GitHub remote + Vercel link (skip if no deploy). manager: draft TASKS.md, commit PLAN.md. | Green repo on GitHub. |
| **T+1 – T+3** | sde(A): dataset pullers (NOAA, NSRDB, EIA, EVI-Pro). sde(B): OpenDSS loader for IEEE 123. sde(C): feature pipeline skeleton. ml-trainer: compose smoke-train notebook (1% data). | `data/features/*.parquet` populated; IEEE 123 loads power-flow cleanly; TFT smoke-train runs on Colab. |
| **T+3 – T+6** | ml-trainer: full MTGNN training run on Colab L4 (24h/15-min horizon). ml-trainer (parallel): TFT training on same split. sde: dashboard scaffold (empty tabs + navigation). | `models/mtgnn_v1.pt`, `models/tft_v1.ckpt`, `reports/mtgnn_v1.md`, `reports/tft_v1.md`. |
| **T+6 – T+8** | sde: power-flow wrapper + decision engine + metrics module. ml-trainer: iterate if metrics are ugly. reviewer: sweep. | Physics check running; flagged feeders list generated. |
| **T+8 – T+12** | sde: full dashboard implementation — map + chart + scenario + metrics. ui-verifier: drives dashboard end-to-end. | `streamlit run app/streamlit_app.py` → full working UI on localhost:8501. |
| **T+12 – T+16** | **BUFFER** / **SLEEP** for owner. Manager runs reviewer + ui-verifier in background; queues polish items. | Polished tests, clean CI. |
| **T+16 – T+20** | sde: stretch goals — what-if sliders, GNNExplainer, conformal wrapper. ml-trainer: DCRNN baseline + foundation-model zero-shot bakeoff. | Stretch features behind feature flags; benchmark plot. |
| **T+20 – T+22** | sde: polish — README, data manifest, model card. ui-verifier: final screenshot pass. | README publication-ready. |
| **T+22 – T+24** | sde: 5-slide deck + 75-s reel. manager: submission package. | `deck/slides.md` → PDF; `reel/final.mp4`; GitHub tagged `v1.0-submission`. |

