## 8. Risk register

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|---|---|---|---|
| Colab session expires mid-training | HIGH | Medium | Checkpoint every 5 min to Drive; ml-trainer resumes from latest ckpt. Prefer Colab Pro+ for 24h background exec if account has it. |
| ASU Google SSO expired in local Chrome Profile 2 | MED | Blocks Colab | Re-auth via DUO 2FA — ping owner. |
| MTGNN NaN-loss / diverges | MED | High | Gradient clipping at 5.0; reduce LR to 1e-4; fall back to DCRNN. |
| OpenDSSDirect.py install fails on Ubuntu 24.04 | LOW | High | Fallback: dockerized OpenDSS (EPRI image) behind CLI. |
| Dashboard render slow on re-inference | MED | Low | Cache forecasts for baseline; only re-run on slider commit, not drag. |
| Pecan Street approval lands in time | LOW | — | Ignore; EnergyBench substitute stands. |
| Judges question "why synthetic not real APS data?" | MED | Medium | Pre-answer slide: real APS AMI is confidential; our synthetic is calibrated to public AZPS macro-totals (EIA-930) + Phoenix climate (NOAA) + ResStock Maricopa. Bias estimate included. |
| Git-LFS bandwidth cap | LOW | Medium | Host weights on HF Hub instead; commit download URL. |
| 4-core / 8 GB RAM laptop can't run dashboard + OpenDSS | MED | Medium | Precompute scenario outputs to parquet; dashboard only reads; what-if sliders use cached lookup table with 5 ΔT × 5 EV% × 3 PV% = 75 precomputed scenarios. |

