| 35-55s | Drag +10°F slider; map redraws; new violations appear; "interventions: dispatch battery bus 812, transfer 1.8 MW to feeder 22". |
| 55-70s | Physics-check panel showing OpenDSS voltage heatmap. |
| 70-75s | Logo + GitHub URL. |

