## 15. Kickoff checklist (first 30 min after green-light)

```
[ ] 1. Initialize git + GitHub repo (manager dispatches sde)
[ ] 2. Copy PLAN.md + create TASKS.md from template
[ ] 3. Write .env.example, register free keys:
       - NREL  https://developer.nrel.gov/signup/
       - EIA   https://www.eia.gov/opendata/register.php
[ ] 4. Install uv env: `uv venv && uv pip sync requirements.txt`
[ ] 5. Smoke-run `scripts/pull_all.sh` (expect 10-15 min for parquets)
[ ] 6. Verify colab-mcp: restart Claude Code → `mcp__colab__*` tools show up
[ ] 7. Open ASU-profile Chrome with the Colab bridge URL → click Connect → select L4 runtime
[ ] 8. ml-trainer: smoke-train TFT on 1% slice (20-min ceiling)
[ ] 9. Commit + tag `v0.1-scaffolded`
```

